4Geeks Academy offers a course called "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer." This course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge and aims to help them start a career as a data scientist and build their first machine learning models. The course duration is 16 weeks, with three classes per week. Classes are limited to a maximum of 12 people. The instructors for this course include Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena, who are experienced professionals in the field of artificial intelligence and machine learning. The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, statistics, and various powerful libraries. Students will learn to create predictive models, work with supervised and unsupervised learning algorithms, and develop their own AI projects. The course also emphasizes real-life case studies and the use of industry-standard tools. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. For more information about this course, visit the 4Geeks Academy website at [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop